cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with human video motion transfer, which involves computer vision and graphics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses appearance control, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of GANs and deep learning techniques suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
